{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":553,"text":"An image is worth more than a thousand words,"},{"time":4395,"text":"so I'm going to start my talk"},{"time":6522,"text":"by stop talking and show you a few images"},{"time":9190,"text":"that I recently captured."}]},{"cues":[{"time":30712,"text":"So by now, my talk is already 6,000 words long,"},{"time":34742,"text":"and I feel like I should stop here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":36890,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":39310,"text":"At the same time, I probably owe you"},{"time":41131,"text":"some explanation"},{"time":42137,"text":"about the images that you just saw."},{"time":45240,"text":"What I am trying to do as a photographer,"},{"time":47963,"text":"as an artist, is to bring the world"},{"time":50446,"text":"of art and science together."},{"time":53823,"text":"Whether it is an image of a soap bubble"},{"time":56162,"text":"captured at the very moment where it's bursting,"},{"time":58928,"text":"as you can see in this image,"},{"time":61400,"text":"whether it's a universe made of tiny little beads"},{"time":64008,"text":"of oil paint,"},{"time":66506,"text":"strange liquids that behave in very peculiar ways,"},{"time":70849,"text":"or paint that is modeled by centrifugal forces,"},{"time":75115,"text":"I'm always trying to link those two fields together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":79081,"text":"What I find very intriguing about those two"},{"time":81471,"text":"is that they both look at the same thing:"},{"time":84750,"text":"They are a response to their surroundings."},{"time":87574,"text":"And yet, they do it in a very different way."},{"time":91467,"text":"If you look at science on one hand,"},{"time":93514,"text":"science is a very rational approach"},{"time":96937,"text":"to its surroundings,"},{"time":98418,"text":"whereas art on the other hand"},{"time":100507,"text":"is usually an emotional approach to its surroundings."},{"time":104810,"text":"What I am trying to do is I'm trying"},{"time":106827,"text":"to bring those two views into one"},{"time":109468,"text":"so that my images both speak to the viewer's heart"},{"time":113418,"text":"but also to the viewer's brain."},{"time":116612,"text":"Let me demonstrate this based on three projects."}]},{"cues":[{"time":121278,"text":"The first one has to do with making sound visible."},{"time":126332,"text":"Now as you may know,"},{"time":127350,"text":"sound travels in waves,"},{"time":129976,"text":"so if you have a speaker,"},{"time":132299,"text":"a speaker actually does nothing else"},{"time":134348,"text":"than taking the audio signal,"},{"time":136232,"text":"transform it into a vibration,"},{"time":139829,"text":"which is then transported through the air,"},{"time":142530,"text":"is captured by our ear,"},{"time":144392,"text":"and transformed into an audio signal again."},{"time":147933,"text":"Now I was thinking,"},{"time":149779,"text":"how can I make those sound waves visible?"},{"time":153999,"text":"So I came up with the following setup."},{"time":156115,"text":"I took a speaker, I placed a thin foil"},{"time":159835,"text":"of plastic on top of that speaker,"},{"time":162070,"text":"and then I added tiny little crystals"},{"time":164737,"text":"on top of that speaker."},{"time":166714,"text":"And now, if I would play a sound through that speaker,"},{"time":169614,"text":"it would cause the crystals to move up and down."},{"time":173496,"text":"Now this happens very fast,"},{"time":175795,"text":"in the blink of an eye,"},{"time":177747,"text":"so, together with LG, we captured this motion"},{"time":181434,"text":"with a camera that is able"},{"time":183120,"text":"to capture more than 3,000 frames per second."},{"time":186595,"text":"Let me show you what this looks like."}]},{"cues":[{"time":190068,"text":"(Music: \"Teardrop\" by Massive Attack)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":231406,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":236724,"text":"Thank you very much."},{"time":237987,"text":"I agree, it looks pretty amazing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":241231,"text":"But I have to tell you a funny story."},{"time":243590,"text":"I got an indoor sunburn doing this"},{"time":246104,"text":"while shooting in Los Angeles."},{"time":248152,"text":"Now in Los Angeles, you could get a decent sunburn"},{"time":250427,"text":"just on any of the beaches,"},{"time":252153,"text":"but I got mine indoors,"},{"time":254223,"text":"and what happened is that,"},{"time":255932,"text":"if you're shooting at 3,000 frames per second,"},{"time":258753,"text":"you need to have a silly amount of light, lots of lights."},{"time":263242,"text":"So we had this speaker set up,"},{"time":265771,"text":"and we had the camera facing it,"},{"time":267370,"text":"and lots of lights pointing at the speaker,"},{"time":270756,"text":"and I would set up the speaker,"},{"time":272111,"text":"put the tiny little crystals on top of that speaker,"},{"time":275157,"text":"and we would do this over and over again,"},{"time":277978,"text":"and it was until midday that I realized"},{"time":280739,"text":"that I had a completely red face"},{"time":283076,"text":"because of the lights pointing at the speaker."},{"time":286162,"text":"What was so funny about it was that"},{"time":288468,"text":"the speaker was only coming from the right side,"},{"time":291195,"text":"so the right side of my face was completely red"},{"time":294562,"text":"and I looked like the Phantom of the Opera"},{"time":296404,"text":"for the rest of the week."}]},{"cues":[{"time":299246,"text":"Let me now turn to another project"},{"time":301349,"text":"which involves less harmful substances."},{"time":307852,"text":"Has anyone of you heard of ferrofluid?"},{"time":311492,"text":"Ah, some of you have. Excellent."},{"time":314014,"text":"Should I skip that part?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":315891,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":317473,"text":"Ferrofluid has a very strange behavior."},{"time":320736,"text":"It's a liquid that is completely black."},{"time":322988,"text":"It's got an oily consistency."},{"time":325482,"text":"And it's got tiny little particles of metal in it,"},{"time":328942,"text":"which makes it magnetic."},{"time":331081,"text":"So if I now put this liquid into a magnetic field,"},{"time":334634,"text":"it would change its appearance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":337427,"text":"Now I've got a live demonstration over here"},{"time":341222,"text":"to show this to you."},{"time":347533,"text":"So I've got a camera pointing down at this plate,"},{"time":350486,"text":"and underneath that plate, there is a magnet."},{"time":354014,"text":"Now I'm going to add some of that ferrofluid"},{"time":357006,"text":"to that magnet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":365609,"text":"Let's just slightly move it to the right"},{"time":373330,"text":"and maybe focus it a little bit more. Excellent."}]},{"cues":[{"time":378088,"text":"So what you can see now is that"},{"time":380281,"text":"the ferrofluid has formed spikes."},{"time":382678,"text":"This is due to the attraction and the repulsion"},{"time":386031,"text":"of the individual particles inside the liquid."},{"time":389740,"text":"Now this looks already quite interesting,"},{"time":391983,"text":"but let me now add some watercolors to it."},{"time":395537,"text":"Those are just standard watercolors"},{"time":397991,"text":"that you would paint with."},{"time":399622,"text":"You wouldn't paint with syringes,"},{"time":400965,"text":"but it works just the same."},{"time":418798,"text":"So what happened now is,"},{"time":420910,"text":"when the watercolor was flowing into the structure,"},{"time":424154,"text":"the watercolors do not mix with the ferrofluid."},{"time":427505,"text":"That's because the ferrofluid itself"},{"time":429841,"text":"is hydrophobic."},{"time":432024,"text":"That means it doesn't mix with the water."},{"time":434187,"text":"And at the same time, it tries to maintain its position"},{"time":437196,"text":"above the magnet,"},{"time":438561,"text":"and therefore, it creates those amazing-looking"},{"time":441956,"text":"structures of channels and tiny little ponds"},{"time":445289,"text":"of colorful water paint."},{"time":447869,"text":"So that was the second project."}]},{"cues":[{"time":449620,"text":"Let me now turn to the last project,"},{"time":451972,"text":"which involves"},{"time":456744,"text":"the national beverage of Scotland."},{"time":458834,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":461154,"text":"This image, and also this one,"},{"time":465074,"text":"were made using whiskey."},{"time":468345,"text":"Now you might ask yourself,"},{"time":469835,"text":"how did he do that?"},{"time":470863,"text":"Did he drink half a bottle of whiskey"},{"time":472712,"text":"and then draw the hallucination he got"},{"time":475423,"text":"from being drunk onto paper?"},{"time":479037,"text":"I can assure you I was fully conscious"},{"time":481281,"text":"while I was taking those pictures."}]},{"cues":[{"time":484391,"text":"Now, whiskey contains 40 percent of alcohol,"},{"time":488493,"text":"and alcohol has got some very interesting properties."},{"time":492729,"text":"Maybe you have experienced"},{"time":494420,"text":"some of those properties before,"},{"time":496546,"text":"but I am talking about the physical properties,"},{"time":499265,"text":"not the other ones."},{"time":501500,"text":"So when I open the bottle, the alcohol molecules"},{"time":505700,"text":"would spread in the air,"},{"time":507043,"text":"and that's because alcohol is a very volatile substance."},{"time":511123,"text":"And at the same time, alcohol is highly flammable."},{"time":515810,"text":"And it was with those two properties"},{"time":517959,"text":"that I was able to create the images"},{"time":520564,"text":"that you're seeing right now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":522594,"text":"Let me demonstrate this over here."},{"time":532709,"text":"And what I have here is an empty glass vessel."},{"time":536027,"text":"It's got nothing in it."},{"time":537336,"text":"And now I'm going to fill it with oxygen"},{"time":541144,"text":"and whiskey."},{"time":559962,"text":"Add some more."},{"time":566171,"text":"Now we just wait for a few seconds"},{"time":568186,"text":"for the molecules to spread inside the bottle."},{"time":571233,"text":"And now, let's set that on fire."}]},{"cues":[{"time":573630,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":591740,"text":"So that's all that happens."},{"time":593278,"text":"It goes really fast, and it's not that impressive."},{"time":596477,"text":"I could do it again to show it one more time,"},{"time":599083,"text":"but some would argue that this is a complete waste"},{"time":601814,"text":"of the whiskey, and that I should rather drink it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":605666,"text":"But let me show you a slow motion"},{"time":607754,"text":"in a completely darkened room"},{"time":609449,"text":"of what I just showed you in this live demonstration."},{"time":621605,"text":"So what happened is that the flame"},{"time":624338,"text":"traveled through the glass vessel from top to bottom,"},{"time":628330,"text":"burning the mix of the air molecules"},{"time":631379,"text":"and the alcohol."},{"time":633208,"text":"So the images that you saw at the beginning,"},{"time":636024,"text":"they are actually a flame stopped in time"},{"time":640368,"text":"while it is traveling through the bottle,"},{"time":642846,"text":"and you have to imagine"},{"time":644064,"text":"it was flipped around 180 degrees."},{"time":647530,"text":"So that's how those images were made."}]},{"cues":[{"time":649968,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":654324,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":657097,"text":"So, I have now showed you three projects,"},{"time":660180,"text":"and you might ask yourself, what is it good for?"},{"time":662832,"text":"What's the idea behind it?"},{"time":664423,"text":"Is it just a waste of whiskey?"},{"time":665756,"text":"Is it just some strange materials?"},{"time":669981,"text":"Those three projects, they're based on very simple"},{"time":672794,"text":"scientific phenomena,"},{"time":674456,"text":"such as magnetism, the sound waves,"},{"time":677197,"text":"or over here, the physical properties of a substance,"},{"time":681239,"text":"and what I'm trying to do"},{"time":683151,"text":"is I'm trying to use these phenomena"},{"time":686300,"text":"and show them in a poetic and unseen way,"},{"time":689417,"text":"and therefore invite the viewer"},{"time":691836,"text":"to pause for a moment"},{"time":693736,"text":"and think about all the beauty"},{"time":696451,"text":"that is constantly surrounding us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":700394,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":701823,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}